1
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:13,799
You're injured.

2
00:01:15,799 --> 00:01:16,519
Let me take a look.

3
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:17,840
No need.

4
00:01:18,359 --> 00:01:19,120
It's just a minor wound.

5
00:01:19,519 --> 00:01:20,680
If you leave it alone,

6
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,719
it will hurt more and more.

7
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:23,760
I'll help you.

8
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,799
The familiar scent.

9
00:01:58,799 --> 00:01:59,359
Right?

10
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,439
Take it to the young lady.

11
00:02:28,639 --> 00:02:29,159
Yes.

12
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,840
It's not bitter at all.

13
00:03:58,919 --> 00:04:00,000
[The shaman said]

14
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,000
[as long as I take the medicine on time,]

15
00:04:02,639 --> 00:04:03,800
[I'll get better.]

16
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:14,719
My Lady,

17
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,720
I had the kitchen make you some

18
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,759
tonic soup.

19
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:22,160
This is really against the rules.

20
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:25,240
But the shaman said it's necessary

21
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,240
to use your blood as a catalyst

22
00:04:27,879 --> 00:04:29,160
to save Ah Fei's life.

23
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:32,519
It's a blessing

24
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,839
to be able to cure her.

25
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,480
My boy,

26
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,720
you've done us a great favor.

27
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,480
The shaman said

28
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:44,399
Ah Fei now has the purest Yang in her.

29
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:46,040
In the future,

30
00:04:46,399 --> 00:04:48,319
her temper will become unpredictable,

31
00:04:48,839 --> 00:04:49,800
and she'll be cruel and vicious.

32
00:04:50,879 --> 00:04:52,040
Please don't blame her.

33
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,279
I understand.

34
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,759
You hate me,

35
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,480
resent me.

36
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:07,040
But protecting me

37
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,480
is still your instinct.

38
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,160
I'm just using you

39
00:05:14,759 --> 00:05:16,000
to investigate the enemy's whereabouts.

40
00:05:19,079 --> 00:05:20,519
Demon wolf, Cang Feng,

41
00:05:22,279 --> 00:05:24,040
you've become so weak now.

42
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,399
It seems that times have changed.

43
00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:29,879
I have freedom,

44
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,600
but you've become timid.

45
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,120
The modern world

46
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:38,519
isn't as good as you think.

47
00:05:39,639 --> 00:05:40,600
All in all,

48
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,639
you still want me to leave.

49
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:48,879
Have a drink with me.

50
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:58,199
This is an order.

51
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:29,000
When you get drunk,

52
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:32,439
your girlfriend can come back.

53
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,680
I never said that.

54
00:06:39,879 --> 00:06:40,920
Isn't it?

55
00:06:42,079 --> 00:06:43,199
You fell in love with her,

56
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:44,920
isn't it because

57
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,720
she has the same face as me?

58
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:53,759
Cang Feng,

59
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,959
I don't know if you are a wolf with a beastly heart,

60
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,360
daring to have desires for your master,

61
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,319
or you love the new life of your enemy

62
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,560
to the point of self-torture?

63
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,839
Crossing the line

64
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:15,079
will be punished.

65
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,319
Kneel.

66
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,639
How dare you disobey my order?

67
00:07:33,199 --> 00:07:35,000
Have you forgotten the blood oath?

68
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,639
The pain of fire burning the skin,

69
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,360
the agony of thousands of ants gnawing at the heart.

70
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,399
If you disobey the order,

71
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:52,560
you will have to suffer such pain,

72
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,519
right?

73
00:07:57,879 --> 00:07:59,040
Good that you know.

74
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:03,360
From the moment you pushed me off the cliff,

75
00:08:03,959 --> 00:08:04,439
no,

76
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:07,439
from the moment you kicked me out of the house,

77
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:08,959
I was no longer Zang Feng.

78
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:11,959
Li Feiyuan,

79
00:08:13,639 --> 00:08:15,319
I'm not your toy.

80
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:19,120
Just because I once wanted to repay a favor,

81
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,160
and was willing to give everything,

82
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:24,079
does that mean I don't deserve dignity,

83
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:26,879
or equal love?

84
00:08:27,959 --> 00:08:29,399
Equal love?

85
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,879
You've really changed.

86
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,440
I won't kill you.

87
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:15,039
This is your last chance for revenge.

88
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:17,879
You drank my blood,

89
00:09:20,039 --> 00:09:21,799
so you became so cruel.

90
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,360
You must be in pain too.

91
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,960
It's too late.

92
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,399
Let it go.

93
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,159
My heart hurts.

94
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:50,440
Li Feiyuan,

95
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:53,440
is your heart hurting?

96
00:10:07,559 --> 00:10:08,080
Jiang Yue,

97
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,000
You were drunk

98
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,039
and slept for a long time.

99
00:10:20,759 --> 00:10:22,360
I heard everything

100
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,679
you said to Li Feiyuan.

101
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,399
You're so loyal to her.

102
00:10:33,759 --> 00:10:35,080
You might as well call me stupid.

103
00:10:36,279 --> 00:10:37,919
You've known her since you were a child.

104
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,639
She even gave you your name.

105
00:10:42,159 --> 00:10:44,039
Of course, she's the only one in your world.

106
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:47,960
You want to protect her,

107
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,720
and you're willing to give her everything,

108
00:10:51,639 --> 00:10:52,759
even your life.

109
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,559
That's not stupid at all.

110
00:10:58,159 --> 00:10:58,799
Lu Zhiyu,

111
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,399
your loyalty

112
00:11:02,879 --> 00:11:04,960
is much more important

113
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,279
than most love in the world.

114
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:22,480
It's dawn.

115
00:11:29,159 --> 00:11:30,759
It seems that every time he gets hurt,

116
00:11:31,519 --> 00:11:32,919
he needs to sleep for a long time.

117
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,080
Maybe

118
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,960
I should be alone and quiet.

119
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,200
I've moved out.

120
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:54,639
Goodbye.

121
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:11,879
Yesterday...

122
00:12:13,279 --> 00:12:14,360
Are you okay yesterday?

123
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:16,159
Who are those people?

124
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,000
I don't know.

125
00:12:18,759 --> 00:12:19,720
But I'm glad you're okay.

126
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:22,799
By the way,

127
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:24,159
where's your bodyguard?

128
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,360
I fired him.

129
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:33,360
Come on,

130
00:12:33,919 --> 00:12:35,120
I'll take you to eat something delicious.

131
00:12:44,679 --> 00:12:45,320
That's enough.

132
00:12:46,559 --> 00:12:47,159
Don't you have anything else

133
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,240
to do?

134
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:49,519
Let me repeat,

135
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:51,519
the boss asked me and Li Si

136
00:12:51,639 --> 00:12:53,960
to monitor you 24/7

137
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,759
and take care of you.

138
00:12:57,919 --> 00:12:59,159
I didn't want to do this.

139
00:13:01,399 --> 00:13:02,039
Me neither.

140
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,480
You're not taking me in,

141
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:06,840
you're putting me under house arrest.

142
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,240
I'm not a criminal.

143
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:10,799
Who told you I have a criminal record?

144
00:13:11,519 --> 00:13:13,120
You should reflect on yourself first.

145
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:15,679
Where's my brother?

146
00:13:16,159 --> 00:13:17,559
Just mind your own business.

147
00:13:18,279 --> 00:13:19,039
Have you seen Jiang Yue?

148
00:13:20,799 --> 00:13:22,120
Didn't you ask us to keep an eye on her?

149
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,320
You were too busy detaining me

150
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:25,120
to notice that she ran away.

151
00:13:25,799 --> 00:13:27,679
What a bunch of stupid dogs!

152
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:28,960
What are you talking about?

153
00:13:29,399 --> 00:13:30,200
Miss Jiang is missing. You two

154
00:13:30,399 --> 00:13:31,080
come with me to find her.

155
00:13:31,279 --> 00:13:31,679
Okay.

156
00:13:32,399 --> 00:13:32,919
A Che

157
00:13:34,919 --> 00:13:35,320
You...

158
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:36,519
Stay here.

159
00:13:41,279 --> 00:13:41,759
Brother,

160
00:13:42,279 --> 00:13:43,440
if you're busy with work,

161
00:13:43,519 --> 00:13:44,759
you don't have to spend the whole day with me.

162
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:47,600
I've canceled all my work for today.

163
00:13:48,159 --> 00:13:49,159
I'm taking a day off.

164
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:50,279
Again.

165
00:13:50,919 --> 00:13:52,399
Every time I just want to have a meal with you,

166
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:54,000
you have to take a whole day off.

167
00:13:54,799 --> 00:13:55,320
Isn't it good?

168
00:13:55,679 --> 00:13:56,639
Of course not.

169
00:13:56,919 --> 00:13:58,320
Then you'll have to work overtime

170
00:13:58,399 --> 00:13:59,240
to deal with the work.

171
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:01,360
It's not a real vacation.

172
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:03,480
Wait.

173
00:14:12,039 --> 00:14:13,120
I don't know which one you like,

174
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,200
so I bought them all.

175
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:17,279
Don't you like them?

176
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,519
I'm not a child anymore.

177
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:21,799
I don't like

178
00:14:21,879 --> 00:14:22,559
these kinds of things

179
00:14:22,679 --> 00:14:23,679
like bears and rabbits.

180
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:26,480
It seems that

181
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,120
you only like dogs.

182
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,080
This is different.

183
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:58,000
Your boss is getting more and more arrogant.

184
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,000
He doesn't even pretend anymore.

185
00:14:59,879 --> 00:15:01,000
How dare he do these smuggling tricks

186
00:15:01,279 --> 00:15:02,320
right under my nose?

187
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:03,879
Isn't he afraid of being caught?

188
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,440
Why should I pretend?

189
00:15:06,159 --> 00:15:09,159
I'm here to marry you openly and aboveboard.

190
00:15:12,559 --> 00:15:13,399
What's your attitude?

191
00:15:13,879 --> 00:15:15,720
Do you not believe in my sincerity

192
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,679
or the financial strength of the Qin family?

193
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:18,799
Qin Yaxin,

194
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:20,840
I don't have time to talk nonsense with you.

195
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:21,840
Please go back.

196
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:25,039
I'll see if you dare to be so rude later.

197
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:26,759
Open it.

198
00:15:36,039 --> 00:15:37,039
Isn't it moving enough?

199
00:15:37,639 --> 00:15:38,159
Fine.

200
00:15:38,919 --> 00:15:39,720
You can pick

201
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:41,600
any gold or jewelry you like

202
00:15:41,879 --> 00:15:42,559
at my home.

203
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:44,799
This is the Noctiluca aurita.

204
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:47,639
You know it.

205
00:15:48,919 --> 00:15:50,480
It's my dad's treasure.

206
00:15:50,919 --> 00:15:52,200
Very rare.

207
00:15:53,039 --> 00:15:54,320
Do you know its other name?

208
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:55,559
What?

209
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:57,639
Life imprisonment snail.

210
00:16:00,919 --> 00:16:02,480
If you don't want to marry me, just say it.

211
00:16:02,639 --> 00:16:04,039
Why slander our family?

212
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:07,600
Forget it.

213
00:16:08,159 --> 00:16:09,360
Forced love is not sweet.

214
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:11,200
I'm a beautiful and kind girl.

215
00:16:11,799 --> 00:16:13,519
You can be my bodyguard.

216
00:16:15,159 --> 00:16:15,759
Who's there?
